// Covers: Product list filter dropdown — category filter removed (fix #37)
//
// Changes tested (fix/v1.2-inventory-frontend):
//   - Category section ("🏷️ <type>") removed from ProductFilterDropdown
//   - `type:` prefix filter values no longer generated by the dropdown
//   - Filter button label still shows "All Products" as default
//   - Remaining general filters (Active, Inactive, Low Stock, Out of Stock,
//     Never Used, Favorites) are unaffected
//
// SUPERSEDES: the Category Filter tests in product-list-ui.cy.js (v1.11 block)
